description:
I really don't get the hype about this place.  I've heard people rave about the Cheese Steak Shop, so I finally decided to give it a try.  I stopped by the place with my teenage little brother, and we both got a classic.  

While my brother loved it (he's a teenager.  He really likes all fast greasy food), I thought it was okay.  It wasn't great, and the portions were kinda eh.  My brother needed a larger one to fill him up; 

Sadly, I can't really tell the difference between this place and the place at the mall, Great Escape.
